Description: Automatically split vinyl recordings into tagged tracks
 VinylSplit analyzes a full-album recording, detects track boundaries,
 identifies tracks using AcoustID and MusicBrainz, embeds metadata and
 artwork, and exports organized FLAC files through both a command-line
 interface and a graphical desktop application.
